title: dryadintro
body:
Congratulations on making it past those awful murderesses...
It's not very lady-like of them don't you think?
Of course, your previous cunning does not mean you will survive this level...
Afterall, death is inevitable...for humans...
Anyway...I call this chapter Gaia's Vengeance!
Here you will encounter all the horrific things Mother Nature throws at human women...
Remember to find me if you need anything...
I'll be much more helpful than that awful Bloody Mary!
I mean, if I feel like it...
[[Thank you...I think... | dryadintrodone ]] [[Alright then... | dryadintrodone]]

title: characterperiod
body:
Oh my Gaia! Are you BLEEDING from *there*?!
I've heard human women do that...
I didn't think it was real though...
How BARBARIC!
[[It's just a period...|characterperiodend]] [[Too bad this building doesn't have tampons!|characterperiodend]]
